OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRishi Sunak's wife to pay  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FUK tax on overseas income  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Chancellor Rishi Sunak's wife Akshata  
OL,6, Murty has said she will pay UK taxes on
OL,7, her overseas income, following a row   
OL,8, over her non-domicile status.          
OL,10,FShe owns #700m in shares of the Indian 
OL,11,FIT giant Infosys, founded by her       
OL,12,Ffather, from which she received #11.6m 
OL,13,Fin dividend income last year.          
OL,15,FAs a non-domiciled (non-dom) UK        
OL,16,Fresident she is not required by law to 
OL,17,Fpay UK taxes on her overseas income.   
OL,19,FBut she told the BBC she did not want  
OL,20,Fto be a "distraction" for her husband. 
